{"tid":1741862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"革命命懸一線 黎明行動刻不容緩","createTime":"2019-11-20T13:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T02:12:21.000Z","uid":331861,"like":39,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5f865deb167c0b7fe99638e989d9b0313cc19971","tid":1741862,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:53:06.000Z","msg":"其實中小學教育界對今次運動嘅貢獻真係超級大，除咗學生set路障同運送物資呢啲主動嘅貢獻之外，其實佢哋嘅被動貢獻更加大，因為好少人意識到<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實佢哋係超級無敵最大嘅流動「路障」！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「路障1」 間接擠塞</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實大家做過學生都應該知道，除非你係超級學霸或者異常勤奮，否則其實都係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">返學等放學，期待假期嗰啲㗎啦</span></span>，而係停課前幾日，我都聽到唔少師弟妹借交通擠塞為由，<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">索性約埋一齊食早餐再慢慢坐巴士先返學，有啲仲會趁熱鬧睇吓啲示威者哥哥姐姐做緊啲咩，流連街頭一陣先算</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「路障2」奴隸父母嘅身心負累</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多父母牢牢碌碌辛苦工作，都係為咗自己仔女嘅生活着想，平時要返學嘅時候可能見到而家社會咁亂，都會<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盡量送埋佢哋返學校先自己再返工</span></span></strong>；而<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">停課期間就更加擔心</span></span></strong>，因為一嚟冇人喺屋企照顧仔女，可能返工都要偷偷地打電話返去，二來係驚佢哋停課期間無所事事，可能出咗去唔知做咩添，所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上星期都聽唔少呢啲父母同事請病假請乜鬼事假諗盡藉口</span></span></strong>去陪個仔或者女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「路障3」光復教畜</span></span></strong><br />\n好多手足都表達過，<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">教畜係其中一種最難提出罷工嘅奴隸之一</span></span></strong>，甚至我頭先都見到有老師到依家仲諗緊點樣起稿寫信叫教協組織遊行，可見呢個行業係今次革命嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">被動性</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但如果學生根本返唔到嚟，甚至好似上星期三咁要停課，咁整間學校都被迫休息</span></span></strong>，好慘<br />\n<br />\n呢三個「路障」真係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好juicy好重要</span></span></strong>，但係要啟動晒呢三個被動加成，就真係有賴大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">準時六點嘅黎明行動</span></span></strong>，因為基本上如果遲過6:30 ，學生同老師都已經出發緊番學校，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個仲要係講緊如果大家係準時行動</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n革命命懸一線，黎明行動刻不容緩，我希望聽日可以準時見到大家，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再俾我聽到啲咩嘆埋個早餐先</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfee46649eed08e426bf834701355fc5297b9ae","tid":1741862,"uid":49827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:56:44.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"e34d2a97abdbb5bdc6a27a9de8b97fff0d120dc0","tid":1741862,"uid":111448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GN07Am6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGN07Am6.png&h=c1b244e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfa2cd36905d3ec043d33694406713e22591fca5","tid":1741862,"uid":49827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b4c971794dec9a0c20f5f026b32d01035d6b86e","tid":1741862,"uid":14667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c269e85b970a068f3f163c35459a1ce356b515ff","tid":1741862,"uid":49827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfa9aec8c8defe854a31014ab1fbddcdcf8eeb2","tid":1741862,"uid":49827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41f50beb0654fc7251dd4dff962c8a23ef60f4b","tid":1741862,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81c14e6806dd6790333e88af1d958f88cadd730","tid":1741862,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:00:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都係影響唔到香港個市<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴又嚟香港上市</span></span>"},{"pid":"61f738f5ef762542dfb186f97d063372432debb7","tid":1741862,"uid":49827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd45d34a1a6c7af94e7b76b61ae5f1529c7a252","tid":1741862,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:01:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2891b5bf1cd82a6e87433977679104a570ce9769","tid":1741862,"uid":49827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"曙光行動 21/11<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/anOxDoU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/anOxDoU</a>"},{"pid":"2d49065fc65484d237cfb0d246eb251a739b41fd","tid":1741862,"uid":49827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor